Stage	Key Characteristics
Manual Operations	"Early Stage of IT Operations
Lack of Operations Tool & Guideline
Reliance on Personal Knowledge, Skill & Experiences"
Procedural Operations	"Growth of Business Surpasses the Growth of Personnel
Create & Manage Documents
Management of Standard Tools"
Automatic Operations	"Growing Differences in Operations Method
Switch from Manual to Automation
Connect Event & Procedure
Visualisation of Operations Data"
DevOps	"Fast Duration, Complex Architecture
Increased Speed & Quality
Online Collaboration Across Teams"
AIOps	"Big Data Accumulation, AI Technology is Ready
Still in the Early Stage
All in the Single Scenario
Goal is to let the Machine to make Decisions"
